# adversarial-artifacts.lst — the SINGLE source of truth for which review artifacts feed
# the status line's ⚔ caught tally. One basename GLOB per line; blank lines and #-comments
# are ignored. count-adversarial-catches.sh reads this; add a line here when a new reviewer
# ships a new artifact so the HUD instrument widens with it (P1-13).
#
# Each glob is matched (via bash `case`) against the BASENAME of a written/edited file.
PR_REVIEW.md
I2P_REVIEW.md
SECURITY-REPORT.md
PII-REPORT.md
DESIGN_REVIEW.md
UI_REVIEW.md
*_INSPECTION_REPORT.md
*_REVIEW.md
